title: Industrial Harbor
description: Step into the world of maritime operations with "Industrial Harbor". This collection offers diverse sound effects and recordings captured within bustling industrial ports.
longDescription:
Step into the world of maritime operations with "Industrial Harbor". This collection offers diverse sound effects and recordings captured within bustling industrial ports, presenting an authentic auditory experience of this unique environment. From the distinctive ambience of the port of Dover to the echoing clangs of equipment at work, this pack allows you to immerse yourself and your players in the soundscape of a busy industrial hub.


One of the standout features of this pack is the "Anchor Hoist" sound. Five minutes of everchanging deep resonance and mechanical friction make a valuable asset for sound designers, providing an impactful auditory element to enhance various projects any game, or any other audio-driven venture, this sound will undoubtedly add a layer of authenticity and depth.
technicalDetails:
Features:

  •  20 Audio WAVS, 20 Audio CUES
  •  16 bit, 44.1 kHz
  •  38+ Minutes
